#for bluetooth and wired earphone run simultaneously

use pavucontrol (gui)or 
pactl list short sinks
pactl load-module module-combine-sink sink_name=combined slaves=alsa_output.pci-0000_00_1f.3.analog-stereo,bluez_output.XX_XX_XX_XX_XX_XX.a2dp-sink
Set the combined sink as default:

bashpactl set-default-sink combined

